according to the terms of this license. SEP also welcomes patches for
improvements or bug fixes to the software.


System Requirements
-------------------
Recommended server requirements:

	* PHP >= 7.4.x (including PHP 5.x) with cURL library support

As SEP does not have the resources to test every possible combination of
software versions and platforms, no guarantee of correct operation or support is
implied. We welcome feedback from users who have deployed this library on
systems other than those listed above.


